snippet.textDisplay: Kachian da honda kacha anjam ni aye gal aam ni. Kacheyan tu rakhiye na umeed paar di. Spritually iska matlab hai k jin logon ka nafs(self) weak hai woh apna task poora nahi kar sakte na hi unko koi mission dia ja skta hai agar dia jaye umeed nahi rakhni chaiye k poora kren ge. Allah k liye ek weak insan yeh nahi kr skta k apne nafs ki khawaishat ko chor ke Allah ka kam kr de. Par channa de disse kulli yaar di. Although Allah is infinite and we Can never truly reach Him but Prophet Muhammad saww Is there As His sign on the other side of the LAKE/OBSTACLE we can see him standing there waiting for us but someone with a weak nafs(ghara) will never get there.
